snippet.title: OUTER WILDS: ECHOES OF THE EYE | Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
There's more to explore here. Coming to PS4, Xbox One, Steam, and Epic Games Store on September 28th. Wishlist on Steam now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1622100?utm_source=youtube&utm_campaign=072921&utm_medium=directreach

A strange satellite photo that can’t be explained. A new museum exhibit that marks the trailhead for one last journey into the wilds. Should you pull at the thread and unravel the solar system’s deepest secret, or is some knowledge better left in the dark?

Developed by MOBIUS DIGITAL. Published by Annapurna Interactive.

© Annapurna Interactive, 2021
